03:56.848 --> 03:58.914
<i>Bless us, O Lord,
and for these gifts</i>

03:58.916 --> 04:00.686
<i>which we are about to receive.</i>

04:01.587 --> 04:04.287
<i>May we pray
that you welcome our neighbours,</i>

04:04.289 --> 04:05.358
<i>who join you now.</i>

04:07.325 --> 04:09.195
We pray, too, for our dad.

04:09.928 --> 04:11.931
Keep him from harm
in the Crimea.

04:13.397 --> 04:15.333
We ask you for his safe return,

04:15.834 --> 04:19.639
so he may join us and
share in your bounty together.

04:20.272 --> 04:22.541
May the Lord
make us truly thankful.

04:23.509 --> 04:24.476
