04:42.594 --> 04:43.629
You were late home.

04:44.363 --> 04:46.432
I had to see
to the animals myself.

04:46.998 --> 04:49.301
And now you've ruined
our supper.

04:50.635 --> 04:52.237
I... I didn't mean to.

04:57.709 --> 04:59.478
Go and get some potatoes
from the pantry.

